title: alterOtherRelationship
prompt: If your work with each contact doesn't fit in these categories, please provide a brief description of the work with each contact.

title: alterCooperate
prompt: How frequently do you cooperate with each contact?
helptext: Cooperation meaning public health leads the collaboration. Planning and implementation are shared but public health controls decision making power and finances)

title: alterCoordinate
prompt: How frequently do you coordinate with each contact?
helpText: Coordination meaning Joint planning and implementation as well as shared resources and decision making

title: alterIntegration
prompt: How frequently do you integrate with each contact?
helptext: Integrate, meaning Collaboratively creating a new policy or program to address a shared goal. There are mutual and shared objectives, shared or new administrative processes. Integration at all stages from design to evaluation
